title: Elon Musk Vs. The World
itunes:title: Elon Musk Vs. The World
description:
Elon Musk's Twitter purchase feels like one of the most momentous transactions in the history of business — but will Musk stay the course? Darren Beattie joins to explain how Musk has the power to bring down America's entire elite regime, but only if he remains firm against unprecedented efforts to shut him down. Plus, he discusses Revolver's latest bombshell January 6 piece, and Herschel Walker explains why he leads in Georgia despite overwhelming efforts to sully his personal character.
